id: Quán lý vũ khí trang bị_CM31

actionConfiguration.body:
SELECT 
q.id,
    q.ten_quan_nhan,
    q.quan_ham,
    q.chuc_vu,
    q.so_dien_thoai,
    d.ten_don_vi
FROM 
    quan_nhan q
LEFT JOIN 
    don_vi d ON q.don_vi_id = d.id
WHERE 
    q.don_vi_id = 9
ORDER BY 
    d.id;
